data.description: This is a Beautiful 3 bedroom, 2 bath pool home with many updated features ready for it's new owners. Modern looking wood-look ceramic tile and 6" baseboards are installed throughout the home. The kitchen has been recently updated including shaker-style cabinets, granite counter tops, stainless appliances, a beautiful glass backsplash and efficient LED can lighting.  The master suite includes a very large walk-in closet. The master bath also is a newer remodel with dual sinks/vanities and tub surround. Enjoy the outdoor space with a dip in the pool or enjoying the large lanai area were there is plenty of room to recline back with your favorite refreshment or BBQ on the grill. The back yard is also fenced in for extra privacy.
